column2: SELECT s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, zp.z, zp.zErr FROM SpecObjAll as s  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN ON s.bestObjID = GN.objID  JOIN Photoz as zp ON zp.objID = s.bestObjID  WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=# ORDER BY distance
